// bisect: fusion/JIT type confusion (soak-jul12n divergence_000001).
// array::map's callback body was [i64, f64], while the downstream sync
// fold settled its result to i64. The instance-body recheck found the
// mismatch but CallSite::setup_bind swallowed it. The interpreter
// returned f64:0; fusion produced no event. The closed return-boundary
// check now rejects the inconsistent callback instance in both modes.
array::fold(array::map([f64:23.5, i64:2, i64:3], |x| x * i64:2), i64:0, |res, v| res / v)
